---
import Layout from '../../layouts/AtelierLayout.astro';
const base='/atelier';
---
<Layout title="About — ATELIER" description="The story behind ATELIER.">
  <section class="wrap" style="max-width:760px;padding:60px 28px 20px;text-align:center">
    <p class="up" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tan);margin-bottom:18px">Our story</p>
    <h1 class="serif" style="font-size:clamp(38px,5vw,60px);font-weight:500;line-height:1.05">Weight you can feel.</h1>
  </section>
  <section class="wrap" style="max-width:680px;padding:30px 28px 60px">
    <div style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.85;color:#4f4940;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:22px">
      <p>ATELIER began with a simple frustration: men's basics that felt like paper and fell apart after a few washes. We wanted the opposite — pieces with weight, structure, and a fit that improves the more you wear them.</p>
      <p>Every tee starts at 240gsm. Hoodies are brushed-back and cut oversized. Our suits are unstructured, made to be worn with a tee underneath, not against it. Nothing here is fast fashion — it is made to be kept.</p>
      <p>We design in small collections, produce in limited runs, and ship worldwide — direct to you.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:40px"><a href={`${base}/contact`} class="btn btn-tan">Get in touch</a></div>
  </section>
</Layout>
